The Foyer~
You stand in the Tower of Clan Circle.  A sense of peace comes over you as 
you stand here.  The walls are made of polished black marble, and the air is 
cool and comforting.  The marble floor is covered with a dark, forest green 
carpet.  At regular intervals on the walls, various hallmarks of Circle's past 
are proudly displayed for all to see.  To the west and east, hallways extend 
around the tower.  An oak door to the north leads outside onto Clan Road.
~
