#4403
The Great Hall~
A massive meeting place, the Great Hall is where grand decisions are made.  
A large wooden table runs down the center of the room.  There are enough chairs 
to seat the entire clan at once.  Seven large, interconnected rings hang above 
the table.  Seven symbolizing the hallowed number of leaders that were ordained 
to be.  Rings symbolizing the unending path of life which we all follow.
Interlinked to symbolize our dependence on each other.  As individuals we 
are weak, but as many we are strong.
~
