#4405
The Great Library of Clan Circle~
The Great Library, wherein lies the collective knowledge and power of the
entire clan.  This massive room is lined, wall-to-wall, with shelves of books, 
most of them written in archaic foreign tongues.  The spellbooks of departed 
clan members are displayed in places of honor around the library.  Tables and 
cots are placed around the room, so that clan members may study and rest 
here if they like.  Clan rumor has it that the power of the library tends to 
enhance the natural curative process.
~
