#4406
The Observatory~
As you reach the top of a narrow staircase you had not seen before, you 
find yourself in a room that is open to the city.  Large circular openings 
in the wall allow the air to drift in.  You can nearly see the whole city 
from this height.  Just south of here the spires of the Temple poke into 
view, while farther away you can see the Midgaard River flowing lazily out 
of the city. To the north you can just see Mt. Olympus on the horizon.  Up 
here, so close to the sky, you feel at one with nature.
~
