The room is very dark and you can almost see the power eminating from the
various portals that lead to unknown regions.  Against the back wall are
several black gates, whose surfaces twist and churn with magical energy,
looking like a whirlpool of black waters.
 
A large metalic plaque beckons for you to read it.
