mirror~
The mirror is aproximately 7 feet high and 5 feet wide.  The frame is
made of a hard metal, which harbors the most intricate designs you
have ever set eyes upon.  Huge snake like dragons are carved into
the frame, circling dozens of hour glasses.  The glass itself is
smooth and untarnished.  Peering into the reflective surface, you
come to realise that shadowy figures seem to be staring back at you
from the other side of the glass.  
~
