#4437
The Observatory~
Located at the very top of the Tower of Clan Circle, the Observatory is a  
massive, semi-circular shaped room.  Slits in the walls allow air to drift in
and out of the room. A planesphere and star chart on the wall help the aspiring
astronomers and astrologers to watch and observe the changing motions of the 
world in the heavens.  The view from here is spectacular.  Just south of the
tower, the spires of the Temple poke into view, while farther away you can see 
the Midgaard River flowing lazily out of the city. To the north you can just 
see Mt. Olympus on the horizon.  So close to the sky, you feel at one with 
nature, and with your own magic.
~
